text: Toney Penna is a proposed Tri-Rail Coastal Link Green Line station in Jupiter, Florida. The station is planned for construction west of Dixie Highway (Broward–Palm Beach) (Florida State Road 811) between Toney Penna Drive and Jupiter Lakes Boulevard. ==References== ==External links== * Proposed site in Google Maps Street View Category:Jupiter, Florida Category:Tri-Rail stations in Palm Beach County, Florida Category:Proposed Tri-Rail stations
